Package: complexviz
Title: Animated Visualizations of Complex Number Concepts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Laurenz", family = "Wiesenberger", email = "laurenz.wiesenberger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Marta", family = "Diaz", email = "martadiazmartieng@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides animated visualizations of key concepts of complex numbers, including addition, multiplication, n-th roots of unity, and polar coordinates, using vector-based graphics with ggplot2 and gganimate.
